#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2656
msgid ""
"This algorithm is intended for use as a means of extracting these useful "
"properties to use as the input values to other algorithms in a model - e.g. "
"to allow to pass an existing raster's pixel sizes over to a GDAL raster "
"algorithm."
